-1 MAP~

From the journals of Lord Gorinae, the Planeswalker...

The overlands seem to be made of two distinct areas, which are
further broken up by oceans.

The first area ("help map1") is more mountainous in nature, while
the other is semi-tropical ("help map2").

I have made no attempt to map the complicated Underdark, the vast
cavernous passages that form a labyrinth under the surface.  The
Underdark is the realm of evil creatures that hate the light
and all who dwell in it.  I feel that such an exploration must
wait until a later date when I can put together a larger and
more powerful expeditionary force.

In addition, there's the entirely different matter of the different
planes of existence.  I cover these in another section of my
journal ("help plane").

~

