Bard are a unique clss, mixing a blend of rogue skills with magical abilities
granted by their music.  Bards are traveling entertainers, telling tales and
singing songs of lore and heroism.

Bards use instruments and song to create magical effects.  The power of their
music may not be as powerful as a mage's magic, but many of the bard's
"spells" are unique to his class and very beneficial to the bard's entire
party.  Bards are truly suited for large groups.

Not even the greatest of bards can sing indefinitely, however, and when the
throat of a bard gets sore, he must rest to regain his strength.  This is
represented by a bard's "mana", which regenerates over time.  Each song a
