0 BLINDFIGHTING~
Reflexive Skill

The blindfighting skill represents the character's ability to fight while
blinded, either because of darkness or other magical means.  High levels of
this skill allow a character to attack and defend himself effectively
without the use of his eyes.
~

0 BLINDNESS~
Spell

Syntax:         cast 'blindness' <target>
Area of Effect: Single target, In-Room
Aggressive:     Yes
Cumulative:     No
Duration:       Short
Type of Spell:  Enchantment

This spell attacks the victim's capacity for sight, cutting off his vision
of the world around him.  Blinded individuals suffer from a number of 
disadvantages, including penalties in melee combat and the inability to
