-1 DUERGAR 'DUERGAR DWARF' DUERGARS~

Duergar, or gray dwarves, are an evil and twisted race, living in the lowest
depths of the Underdark.  Cunning and manipulative, it is said that only the
duergar can match the cruelty and depravity of the drow elves.  They hate all
other races, but have some grudging relations with a few of the other races
of the Underdark.

Duergar, like the mountain dwarves they despise, are inordinately sturdy and
strong.  They have medium to dark gray skin and hair and prefer to wear drab
clothing to blend into their environment.  Duergar have the unique ability to
cloak themselves in darkness, melding into the shadows to become invisible.
