of them, appearing back on the overland map.  

You may also "fly land" to drop to the ground, landing safely there.  Flying
also prevents you from falling in certain rooms where the ground is unstable
(or simply gone).

When you are flying on the overland map, you will only see the "P"s and "Ms"
indicating other players and mobs that are on your own level or altitude.

