0 'GROUP RECALL'~
Spell

Syntax:         cast 'group recall'
Area of Effect: Group, In-Room
Aggressive:     No
Cumulative:     N/A
Duration:       Instant
Type of spell:  Teleportation

This spell will attempt to recall the caster's entire party back to the
caster's home, just like the "Word of Recall" spell.  It will only work
on members that are in the same room as the caster.  However, this spell
is a little bit tricky.  Unlike other group spells which affect everyone
in the caster's party no matter what, this spell will only work on those
that are ABOVE the caster on the 'group' list.  Basically, the spell works
on each person in the group in the order they are listed on the 'group'
list, and when it gets to the caster, he is teleported home.  Since he is
no longer in the same location as the remaining members of the party, the
spell fails to send them home.

Basically, make sure the person that will be casting 'group recall' is
the last person grouped.

WARNING: If any of the people who are recalled are overloaded, there is a
chance that they will drop some equipment.

See also: WORD OF RECALL
