     L. Memory

Shopkeepers can have no affect1/affect2/affect3/affect4 flags.

Shopkeepers must have a race of "H. (humanoid)".
Shopkeepers should have a hometown of "0 (none)".
Shopkeepers should have an alignment of "0".
Shopkeepers should have a class of "0 (none)".

Shopkeepers should have a level of "1".
Shopkeepers should have a position and default position of "8 (standing)".
Shopkeepers can be neuter, male, or female.

Section M. values should be left as the default values of 0.

Shopkeepers cannot have quest information.

Shopkeepers should have the following shop information:

A. List of Items the Shop Sells
     
