-1 RITUALS~

Rituals are a special form of magic, practiced only by druids.  Certain
spells require more power than a single caster can produce.  Multiple
druids, working in concert with one another, can call upon the spirit
of the natural world to do their bidding, producing more powerful effects
than a lone druid could manage.

Most rituals have long casting times, but make up for that hindrance with
longer durations and better effects.

Rituals will have a minimum number of druids that must be involved to cast
the spell.  The druids must be of a certain level.  If more druids of the
appropriate level assist in the casting of the ritual, the spell will
take effect sooner.
~

